{"word":"ὄφελος 1","slug":"ὄφελος 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n76089\" key=\"o)/felos1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὄφελος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀφέλλω</foreign> B) only in nom. and acc. sg., <sense id=\"n76089.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">furtherance, advantage, help</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἴ κ᾽ ὄφελός τι γενώμεθα</foreign> in case we can be of any <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">use</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:236\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.236</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅς τοι πόλλ᾽ ὄ. γένετο</foreign> who was a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">help</tr_> to thee in many matters, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:152\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.152</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδὲν σοί γ᾽ ὄ.</foreign> not as any <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">good</tr_> to thee, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:513\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.513</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄ. τί μοι ἔσσῃ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg004.perseus-grc1:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Merc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τί δ᾽ ἔστ᾽ ὄ. δειλὸς ἀνήρ</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">;</tr_> <bibl n=\"Thgn. 102\" default=\"NO\" TEIform